data.description: Welcome Home! Sellers are giving a $5,000 incentive towards future buyers closing cost. This lovely 5 bedroom 3 bath home with 2601 sqft of spacious living space can be yours to enjoy with family and friends. In the beautiful kitchen you will find nice granite countertops with a beautiful backsplash. All the stainless steel appliances convey including washer and dryer. Upstairs you can enjoy a flex room and make into whatever you like. Don't worry about privacy with this home it is already fenced in for you. Located in a quiet neighborhood with a community pool minutes from Lake Nona. Contact me to schedule a viewing and experience the option of living in beautiful Saint Cloud.
